{
  "stem": "22803.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that is a good question, in the view of it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, you were known in the area.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But also, it is a good question because I must say, only my mother of all the people I know did this.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She thought it was very healthy to go swimming.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she would send me in any case, and nobody interfered with me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I would go to this, to this, you know, pool.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But always, I was a lot by myself because, of course, you know, nobody interfered with me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But on the whole, if it says, no Jews allowed, you really didn't go, which applied to more and more things.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, there were signs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And also more and more friends who I had who were not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like, there was a little boy when we were little living downstairs.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were friends.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, of course, then boys and girls went to separate schools anyway.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So there was less, you know, less time to be together.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But eventually, you know, all these people would keep away from you, even if they were not anti-Semitic per se.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was just sort of understood.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so you became more and more isolated.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, you, you knew that, you know, that there were these regulations and these laws against the Jews.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they became more stringent.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I think people here don't understand that it kept up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It didn't happen all at once.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my parents and their friends, they used to talk, oh, well, you know, that-- that Hitler is a flash in the pan, and we'll outlive this regime.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, you know, and didn't really realize that it was going to be progressively getting worse.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
